ArtyTorrent Pack 74-Tech Trance Drum Loops 130-139bpm-WAV
---------------------------------------------------------

Miscellaneous drum loops for techno and trance.
Tempo ranges from 130-139 bpm.

Torrent contains 3 RAR files with 90 loops
------------------------------------------
DDT 4 on the floor 130-139 (16 loops)
Magix Techno Drums 139 (48 loops)
Misc Tech Trance 130-139 (26 loops)
 
Samples are from a variety of sources including CDs by EastWest, Sony/Sonic Foundry, Elab and Magix, and have all been normalized and acidized as 16-bit WAVs at 44.1KHz. Approx tempo is included in each filename.
